headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Predicting Erie Indemnity Company Stock Will Climb or Sink?
summary: Although Erie Indemnity has underperformed the broader market over the past 52 weeks, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook about the stock’s prospects.
